text: On May 1, 2017, Tax Exempt and Government Entities underwent a reorganization. The new Compliance, Planning & Classiﬁcation function absorbed several groups previously housed in Exempt Organizations Examination Planning and Review, and accepted ownership of this manual. This supersedes IRM 4.75.8, Exempt Organizations Examination Procedures, Compliance Strategies and Critical Initiatives, dated September 9, 2016.
